{"id":103821,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/09/中国版寂静岭：小汤山非典医院-当时我就震惊了（/","date":"2010-09-10T21:10:36Z","modified":"2010-09-10T21:11:26Z","title":"中国版寂静岭：小汤山非典医院 当时我就震惊了（图）","content":"<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3888816/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/23/180023.33971554_500.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\n<div>位于北京以北35公里的小汤山镇，这个素有“温泉古镇”之美称的京北重镇，因为6年前“小汤山非典定点医院”的存在，一夜间让世界知晓。</div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3888817/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/23/180023.79692660_500.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div>这座7天7夜赶建而成的占地2.5万平方米的临时建筑曾被世界卫生组织专家称之为：“世界医疗史上的奇迹”。</div>\n<div>\n<div><img src=\"http://img21.mtime.cn/mg/2010/08/23/180624.22828029.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n<div>如今医院早已人去屋空，除了院子里的灌木和杂草，这里看不到任何生机与生气。</div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3888822/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/23/180024.25623895_500.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3888819/\"><br />\n</a></div>\n<div>跟细菌战一般</div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3888827/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/23/180026.21901834_500.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3888828/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/23/180027.15857637_500.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3888829/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/23/180028.53558740_500.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3888828/\"><br />\n</a></div>\n<div>宛如灾难之后的惨状</div>\n<div><a href=\"http://i.mtime.com/903833/photo/3888843/\"><img src=\"http://img22.mtime.cn/up/2010/08/23/180033.59115754_500.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div>&#8230;&#8230;.</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://dangzhongyang.info\" target=\"_blank\">“要翻墙，用赛风”</a>.</p>\n","author":1,"categories":[20534],"tags":[14277,8800]}